item.description:
Thanks Terri for all your help and fun during the past several years. Let's all get together to talk about we want to do next with our meet up group.
Let's meet at Paneras in Bishops corner in west hartford. Let's meet 6/20 at 7pm. All are welcome. I am seeking both ideas and organizers for dinners, sports, theatre, business events.

sorry about change but there was a fee for me to hold a room in other place.
You can reach me at 5083803737, unfortunately please don't text.
Our thank you party for Terri will be at Gouveia Vineyards sunday june 17 at 2pm in wallingford, please join us

thanks
Nancy Frede
soulpart@aol.com
